Package: gert
Type: Package
Title: Simple Git Client
Version: 0.1
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen@berkeley.edu>
Description: Simple git client for R based on 'libgit2' <https://libgit2.org/>. This
    package requires that a somewhat recent version of 'libgit2' is installed on the
    system.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: libgit2 (>= 0.26): libgit2-devel (rpm) or libgit2-dev (deb)
URL: http://github.com/jeroen/gert (devel), https://libgit2.org (upstream)
BugReports: http://github.com/jeroen/gert/issues
